Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年SUNDAY特制DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名侦探柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说 这个礼拜天早上10点 大家来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露营
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 不是上次刚刚露营过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要露营应该比这个时间更早集合不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去赏樱花吧 堤无津河边的樱花已经盛开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是开发了新的游戏软件 拜托我们去试试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定没什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自阿笠博士的挑战书!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠VS柯南&少年侦探团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致侦探们 我被坏人抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到米花镇的三个地方去找找看 来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个地点从帝丹小学要走5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从米花车站要走10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东都塔要走15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的水楢树下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饿着肚子在那里等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要马上去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这是博士给我们设计的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:01:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧 灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是昨天晚上他一个人偷偷弄到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摊着米花镇的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花镇的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样 是给我们猜的谜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 原来不是绑架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个谜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被抓了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这作为游戏的设定我可不敢苟同噢 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原 那张米花镇的地图呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们大家一起快点想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士说他一个人干的 这次你没帮他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次我不知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤 我想你应该猜出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但难得博士这次高兴地出了题目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就帮那些孩子们解下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不给点提示的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小学一年级的学生来说太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是帝丹小学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是米花车站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家就算了 找找东都塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 但是从小学那里走5分钟会走到哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不是我们5个人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都要走5分钟以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用跑的话就不用5分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个题目难的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方还要离米花车站10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东都塔还要走15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从米花车站走10分钟 从东都塔走15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些条件如果不是时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是距离的话 就简单一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦 大致来说 时间转换成距离是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人行走的速度是大致是每小时4-5千米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房产广告中好像是每分钟80米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每分钟80米 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分钟是400米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟是800米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15分钟是1200米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个地图的比例尺是10000：1的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,400米是4厘米 800米是8厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1200米是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦 这里有尺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离帝丹小学4厘米的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离米花车站8厘米的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么 也带我参加嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 离东都塔12厘米的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 为什么不是一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个告诉他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 再看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 用了这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆规 以前看过姐姐用过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个圆圈里的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离帝丹小学5分钟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离米花车站10分钟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离东都塔12分钟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花公园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水楢树 水楢树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水楢树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和管理员叔叔说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个树下有第二个题目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往右边一点 右边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a ga sa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是博士的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这说不定是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,agasa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a ga sa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a kasa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a gasa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑话冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么写在上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上面都是字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,n yu e u te sa ka ne ro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su ko ki yo se ta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mo na o shi mi ra re ri ma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to tsu ni me he a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都像是暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暗号是用来提示第二个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒过来读读试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a he me ni tsu to ma ri
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔一个跳着读读看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,n me te ka ro ka ro ko yo ta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 太棒了（genta kun su te ki yo）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么读的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得是这么读的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带子是绑在伞上的 我对这件事比较在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带子上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 把这个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 你弄反了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这个地方也是提示的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字排列起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a ma o ki sa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,e ri na ko te
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,me re mo su u
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ni ra ta ro e
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tsu mi se ne yu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to shi yo ka n
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才丝带上的谜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种古希腊真实使用过的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做Scytale
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.74,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Scytale：古希腊斯巴达的密码棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scytale
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在一定粗细的棒子上绑上皮绳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把文字写在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还知道得真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探的话谁都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说你 是那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不觉中一点一点长了知识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐和园子姐姐为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 我们来图书馆很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰就算了 你就太不合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小兰姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶色头发的姐姐也在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁是茶色头发的姐姐 要叫园子姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才阿笠博士来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士找到了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 帮我把这个给孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说你们过30分左右就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 不是大不了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 〇〇〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有〇〇〇〇一样的容貌 还只有53岁〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是〇〇里面要填词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把红色〇〇的词排列一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以知道第三个地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容貌是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是脸长什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从开头的4个文字开始考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 〇〇〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是一直说 我是天才的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是 有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 有钱人 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 独身 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有钱人的话 就是穷人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是性格上的 顽固 之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他戴着眼睛 是近视 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是老花眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅哥 应该不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是脸的话 就是圆圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是大鼻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了元太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们要搞到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑就算了 这些都和答案没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要依次考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得果然是 天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 大鼻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧 那个之后再慢慢讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看后面的4个字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的4个字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有〇〇〇〇一样的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容貌的话 就是指长相 我有老人的容貌 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 老头子 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成元太的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有不同意见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就看最后的2个字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只有53岁〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只有53岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前的4个文字如果是 老人 的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是爷爷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花神社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是先预约一下的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说 最开始的四个字是顽固啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圆脸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦 肯定是粗眉毛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还在争论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到了神社就能见到他本人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案直接问问他不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是博士的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急刹车的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有车身擦过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 被车撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果是被车撞了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜应该掉落在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比这个刹车痕迹更前面一点的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 并没有发现车子的零件 油漆什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法确定什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但博士肯定是发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 会不会是游戏的继续呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士确实写着找到米花镇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个地方后来救我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会不会是表示自己在第三个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 博士可能是打算在米花神社和大家碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一起去吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在米花神社附近有一个不错的饭店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张广告纸他也看过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪他说饿着肚子等着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先打博士的手机看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 博士如果拿着侦探徽章就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徽章我给了博士了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把徽章忘在衣服口袋里 被妈妈洗掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有点坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 在书店门口遇到博士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他帮我修好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件外衣他今天也穿着的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 徽章现在也可能在他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 在西南方向2公里处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是没有修好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对讲机功能可能还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是博士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 柯南吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 游戏变成真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你被谁绑架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀 犯人是一对年轻的男女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们绑架了一个中学生模样的女孩子放在车上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他们电击晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在被监禁在某个大楼里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人和那个女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都在隔壁的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们刚刚打了要求赎金的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快救她的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你那里是什么大楼知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但是窗户有个缝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以看到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个电线杆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电线杆的后面好像藏着一个穿着蓝衣服的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他能看到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没戴眼镜看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我在的地方是2楼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到什么吗 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音的话 好像听到有些很吵闹的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那种嘀嘀呱呱 唧唧咕咕的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是犯人进屋了什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快的话 博士的性命有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里西南2公里的地方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米花镇四丁目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只能靠博士说的线索寻找了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是没有人的大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕可能是高层大楼或者是还在修建的大楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电线杆的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士也说过藏着一个穿蓝衣服的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是有人在监视博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 博士也说过2个犯人都在隔壁的屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意跑到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电线杆的后面来监视似乎不大可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士听到那个声音是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像说是嘀嘀呱呱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说了唧唧咕咕的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是青蛙呢 还是鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 总之先找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去报警
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来驱赶乌鸦的网
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士没戴眼镜看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到系在电线杆后面的网兜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去不是像藏着一个穿着蓝衣服的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到挂着这样的网的电线杆就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是放垃圾的有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只能找找看了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 关于博士说的那种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是蝉的叫声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉不是夏天才叫的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有蝉是在春天鸣叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫春蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每天的10点到14点间太阳出来的时候鸣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐声鸣叫是它们的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐声鸣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只叫起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它周围的蝉都会一齐叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 它们的另外一个特征就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有松树林的附近才有这种蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松树林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这里附近好像没什么松树林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有一个地方有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确呢 说不定就是这个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了以前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为做春蝉课题的研究曾经来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 光彦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那边的电线杆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蓝色网兜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要到收钱的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位小姐可是我非常重要的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这位爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是个麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然看上去头发花白像爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还只有53岁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川柯南 是个侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 看我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿治
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用驱赶乌鸦的网
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绑架犯抓住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你们会来救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可要给我们一些容易明白的提示哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.49,0:24:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店的感觉还真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 这可是住宅街中的标志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是像那种秘密基地的店一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.43,0:24:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们就把这里当成
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.96,0:24:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年侦探团的秘密基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.73,0:24:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了 这里不过就是一家西餐厅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.24,0:24:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个不错的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.19,0:24:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭菜很好吃 卫生间很干净
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且老板还是一对美女姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都来光顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:24:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是不能当作秘密基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.65,0:25:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰不会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.07,0:25:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先去告诉小兰吧
